<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">
  <tal:block metal:use-macro="context/@@groupserver_layout/page">
    <head>
      <title metal:fill-slot="title">
        <tal:block replace="view/label" />:
        <tal:block replace="view/groupInfo/name" />:
        <tal:block replace="view/siteInfo/name"/>
      </title>
    </head>
    <body>
      <div metal:fill-slot="body">
        <h1 tal:content="view/label"><span tal:replace="view/userInfo/name"/></h1>
        <!--Summarise what has gone wrong -->
        <div id="summary">
          <h4>What's the problem?</h4>
          <p>
            The <span class="group" tal:content="view/groupInfo/name"/> member 
            <span tal:replace="view/userInfo/name"/> currently has no verified 
            email addresses.  
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Tell the admin what they can do -->
        <div id="explanation">
          <h4>What can be done?</h4>  
          <p>
            If you have the means to contact <span tal:replace="view/userInfo/name"/>
            in real life, please ask them to add a new email address to their profile.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Give an explanation about what went wrong -->
        <div id="explanation">
          <h4>What went wrong?</h4>
          <p>
            It is likely that <span tal:replace="view/userInfo/name"/>'s email 
            address was consistently rejecting messages, and was reset to  
            "unverified" as result. It is also possible that
            <span tal:replace="view/userInfo/name"/> has never verified an address.
          </p>
          <ul tal:repeat="address view/emailAddresses">
            <label>Details for <code class="email" tal:content="address"/></label>
            <li tal:condition="not:view/bounceHistory/?address">
              Sorry, but unfortunately no details are available 
              for <code class="email" tal:content="address"/>.
            </li>
            <li tal:repeat="event view/bounceHistory/?address">
              <span tal:replace="structure event"/>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
  </tal:block>
</html>


